EEE4160_Capstone_Design — Licensing Notice
===========================================

This repository aggregates two independently licensed components. Each
retains its original upstream license in its own subdirectory:

  gem5/      BSD 3-Clause License
             See gem5/LICENSE.

  rocksdb/   Dual-licensed under GPL-2.0 OR Apache-2.0 (at your option).
             See rocksdb/COPYING (GPLv2) and rocksdb/LICENSE.Apache.
             LevelDB-derived portions: see rocksdb/LICENSE.leveldb.

No combined or statically linked binary of the two components is produced
or distributed from this repository: the simulator (gem5) and the database
(RocksDB) are built and run as separate programs. Each component is governed
solely by the license in its own subdirectory.

Project-specific additions authored for EEE4160 — including gem5/src/dev/pnm,
gem5/configs/yonsei, and the rocksdb/tools/pnm_* files — are released under
the same license as the component in which they reside.
